org.graphity.server.model

Class GraphStoreBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.graphity.server.model.GraphStoreBase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.hp.hpl.jena.graph.FrontsNode, com.hp.hpl.jena.rdf.model.RDFNode, com.hp.hpl.jena.rdf.model.Resource, GraphStore

    public class GraphStoreBase
extends Object
implements GraphStore
    Proxy implementation of SPARQL Graph Store. This class does not natively manage the RDF store. It forwards the requests to a remote Graph Store service.
